prompt.title: Embedding for Book Language: Readable Markdown Subset
prompt.content: The Book language is a subset of markdown designed to be easily readable by both humans and machines. It uses .book file extension and UTF-8 encoding. There are two variants: flat (single prompt) and full (structured with tasks, commands, and prompts).
